t-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">旗手篇</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=o0174bo5i0d&tiny=0&auto=0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; width: 510px; height: 497px;\"></iframe></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">哎哟篇</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2015年，澳大利亚最大的葡萄酒品牌夏迪，第二次成为英国板球赛的赞助商。这对于英国本土人来说，可不算是个好消息——毕竟英国是澳大利亚的宗主国。于是，在这一系列广告中，赞助商的品牌被各种嫌弃。毕竟没有比看澳洲人滚蛋，更能让英国板球迷高兴的了。看来为了讨好英国人，广告主也是豁出去了。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">挪威Telenor电信公司：孩子的爱情</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">代理商：Try广告公司</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=k0174zgazvn&tiny=0&auto=0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; width: 510px; height: 497px;\"></iframe></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“爱你在心口难开”，说的就是片中这个挪威小孩，明明深爱着对方，却怯于开口。而且女孩搭乘的飞机在40分钟后就要起飞，显然来不及。所幸他有一帮神队友：家里的长辈们热心地开车奔赴机场，想要促成这对小情侣。奈何本来就狭窄的道路，却被一群绵羊堵死了。长辈们纷纷下车搬羊，小孩脑中灵光一闪：咱们这里不是覆盖有4G网络么？于是，网络帮助了一对有情人，女孩回应说：“Yes！”</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Canal数字电视：小丑/电锯</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">代理商：TBWA，斯德哥尔摩</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=g0174y0qot4&tiny=0&auto=0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; width: 510px; height: 497px;\"></iframe>&nbsp;<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.5;\">小丑篇</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=g0174mtffku&tiny=0&auto=0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; width: 510px; height: 497px;\"></iframe>&nbsp;<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.5;\">电锯篇</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一群戴着小丑面具的劫匪闯入银行，欲行抢劫。职员个个呆若木鸡，唯独一个女职员特别开心，邀请“小丑”进入柜台表演节目，结果可想而知；即将入睡的丈夫，突然发现花园里有一个人，手持电锯。“啊哈！他可以帮咱们放到那棵桦树！”丈夫兴冲冲地穿上外套，出门询问时价去了……呆萌可能连命都保不住。想要不做蠢事？还是多看电视吧。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">阿根廷肝脏移植基金会：老人与爱犬</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">代理商：DDB，阿根廷</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=g0174hjd1of&tiny=0&auto=0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; width: 510px; height: 497px;\"></iframe></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">熟悉的背景音乐响起，观众想必能猜出这是一个什么故事。孑然一身的老人，身边唯有狗狗陪伴。无数个美好的日子过去，老人的生命也走到了尽头。狗狗在病房外苦苦守候，最终却扑进一位陌生女士的怀抱。原来，老人的器官移植给了这位女士，小狗也有了新的感情归宿。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Juva Santé基金会：不管发生什么事</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">代理商：Havas 360，皮托</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=j0174irk3h3&tiny=0&auto=0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; width: 510px; height: 497px;\"></iframe></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">电梯篇</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=u0174mmkepa&tiny=0&auto=0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; width: 510px; height: 497px;\"></iframe></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">新鞋篇</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=v0174vp8len&tiny=0&auto=0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; width: 510px; height: 497px;\"></iframe></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">少年篇</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">陌生男女遭遇电梯事故，接下来会发生什么呢？不管发生什么事，广告主早已为你准备好了口腔喷雾剂、润唇膏、凡士林、抗菌湿纸巾，甚至验孕棒；拿到新鞋难免激动地尖叫，接下来要做什么呢？广告主同样准备了足贴、足底护理剂、液体创可贴、除臭剂以及，耳塞；牙套女孩闭上眼睛，激动地迎接男友的初吻，接下来要怎么做呢？治疗口腔溃疡的液体创可贴、口腔喷雾剂、牙签、牙线，以及疱疹贴。这服务得有多周到啊！</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">杜蕾斯：到达</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">代理商：Havas，伊斯坦布尔</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://image.meihua.info:808/editor/2015/12/03/20151203112154_526.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"424\" title=\"\" align=\"\" class=\"mycls\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://image.meihua.info:808/editor/2015/12/03/20151203112156_374.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"424\" title=\"\" align=\"\" class=\"mycls\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这是为杜蕾斯新品“Mutual Climax”创作的平面。顾名思义，这款避孕套能让双方都达到高潮。而在广告中，代理商模拟了火车站和机场的场景，而其中一方比另一方（指示牌上的名字，不难猜出男或女）获得了生命中更大的和谐。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.760784); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">来源：<a href=\"http://www.adquan.com/post-1-32750.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 141, 212); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease; background-color: transparent;\">广告门</a><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/>原作者：冯琪</p><p><br/></p>', '', '', '/84/90\\95.html', '', '0', '1549');
INSERT INTO `cms_article` VALUES ('96', '8', '<p><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:20px\">S</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:20px\">truts2</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background:rgb(0,255,255);background:rgb(0,255,255)\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;background:rgb(0,255,255);background:rgb(0,255,255)\">S</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;background:rgb(0,255,255);background:rgb(0,255,255)\">truts2的介绍:基于mvc的web框架.</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;background:rgb(0,255,255);background:rgb(0,255,255)\">2.mvc的定义:控制器丶模型丶视图.一直设计典型.</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;background:rgb(0,255,255);background:rgb(0,255,255)\">3.struts2是webWork继承而来.</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;background:rgb(0,255,255);background:rgb(0,255,255)\">4.</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;background:rgb(0,255,255);background:rgb(0,255,255)\">struts.properties</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">是struts2框架的全局属性文件,自动加载.(键值对).</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;background:rgb(0,255,255);background:rgb(0,255,255)\">5.web.xml</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas;font-size: 19px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&lt;</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(63,127,127);font-size:19px\">filter</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&gt;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas;font-size: 19px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&lt;</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(63,127,127);font-size:19px\">filter-name</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas;font-size: 19px\">struts2</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&lt;/</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(63,127,127);font-size:19px\">filter-name</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&gt;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&lt;</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(63,127,127);font-size:19px\">filter-class</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas;font-size: 19px\">org.apache.struts2.dispatcher.ng.filter.StrutsPrepareAndExecuteFilter</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&lt;/</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(63,127,127);font-size:19px\">filter-class</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&gt;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas;font-size: 19px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&lt;/</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(63,127,127);font-size:19px\">filter</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&gt;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(63,95,191);font-size:19px\">&lt;!--&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">项目第一次加载</span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas\">web.xml&nbsp;--&gt;</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas;font-size: 19px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&lt;</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(63,127,127);font-size:19px\">filter-mapping</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&gt;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas;font-size: 19px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&lt;</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(63,127,127);font-size:19px\">filter-name</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas;font-size: 19px\">struts2</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&lt;/</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(63,127,127);font-size:19px\">filter-name</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&gt;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas;font-size: 19px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(63,95,191);font-size:19px\">&lt;!--&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">所有的请求都会经过</span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas\">struts2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的过滤器&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas\">--&gt;</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas;font-size: 19px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&lt;</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(63,127,127);font-size:19px\">url-pattern</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas;font-size: 19px\">/*</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&lt;/</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(63,127,127);font-size:19px\">url-pattern</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&gt;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas;font-size: 19px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&lt;/</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(63,127,127);font-size:19px\">filter-mapping</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&gt;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas;font-size: 19px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&lt;</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(63,127,127);font-size:19px\">welcome-file-list</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&gt;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas;font-size: 19px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&lt;</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(63,127,127);font-size:19px\">welcome-file</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family: Consolas;font-size: 19px\">index.jsp</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&lt;/</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(63,127,127);font-size:19px\">welcome-file</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&gt;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:37px\"><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&lt;/</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(63,127,127);font-size:19px\">welcome-file-list</span><span style=\";font-family:Consolas;color:rgb(0,128,128);font-size:19px\">&gt;</span> </p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(255,0,0);font-size:16px\">注:</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(255,0,0);font-size:16px\">&nbsp;struts.properties</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(255,0,0);font-size:16px\">里面的配置可以在struts里面进行配置,可通过&lt;constant&gt;标签完成struts2的配置.</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;background:rgb(0,255,255);background:rgb(0,255,255)\">6.&lt;package&nbsp;name=</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;background:rgb(0,255,255);background:rgb(0,255,255)\">””</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;background:rgb(0,255,255);background:rgb(0,255,255)\">&nbsp;extends=</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;background:rgb(0,255,255);background:rgb(0,255,255)\">””</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;background:rgb(0,255,255);background:rgb(0,255,255)\">&nbsp;namespace=|</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;background:rgb(0,255,255);background:rgb(0,255,255)\">””</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;background:rgb(0,255,255);background:rgb(0,255,255)\">&gt;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&lt;action&nbsp;name=</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">””</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;class=</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">””</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;method=</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">””</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&gt;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&lt;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">result</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;name&gt;jsp页面路径&lt;/result&gt;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&lt;/action&gt;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&lt;/package&gt;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">P</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">ackage的name是package的名字,且是唯一的.extends是继承父package的名称.abstract是设置package的属性为抽象的,抽象的package是不能定义action.&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;background:rgb(0,255,255);background:rgb(0,255,255)\">7.</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&lt;global-results&gt;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&lt;result&nbsp;name=</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">””</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&gt;/error.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&lt;/global_result&gt;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">全局的配置.</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;background:rgb(0,255,255);background:rgb(0,255,255)\">8.Servlet&nbsp;API</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">1.ActionContext.</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">2.action<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">搜索顺序</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">:</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">http://localhost:8080/struts2/path1/path2/student.action</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:80px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:16px\">①.&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">判断</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">package</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">是否存在</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">如</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">:path1</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-left:80px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:16px\">②.&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">如果不存在<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">重复第一步继续查找上一级</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">package</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">路径</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">如存在判断</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">action</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">是否存在</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">如果不存在</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">则去默认</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">namespace</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">package</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">里面查找</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">action</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-left:80px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:16px\">③.&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">如果没有<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">则报错</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">.</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-left:80px\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:16px\">④.&nbsp;</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">动态方法调用</span><img width=\"554\" height=\"81\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor1_3_6/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" word_img=\"file:///C:\\Users\\dev04\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\ksohtml\\wps8BC1.tmp.jpg\" style=\"background:url(http://localhost:8080/ueditor1_3_6/lang/zh-cn/images/localimage.png) no-repeat center center;border:1px solid #ddd\"/> &nbsp; <span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span><img width=\"554\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor1_3_6/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" word_img=\"file:///C:\\Users\\dev04\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\ksohtml\\wps8BC2.tmp.jpg\" style=\"background:url(http://localhost:8080/ueditor1_3_6/lang/zh-cn/images/localimage.png) no-repeat center center;border:1px solid #ddd\"/></p><p style=\"margin-left:56px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">如果<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">action</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">有</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">add</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">方法</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">然后可以找到</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">helloworld</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">方法</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">可以对应的找到</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">add.jsp.</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-left:56px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">⑤<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">默认</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">action</span></span> </p><p style=\"margin-left:56px;text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">当找不到<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">action</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">默认跳到这里</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-left:56px;text-indent:28px\"><img width=\"554\" height=\"117\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor1_3_6/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" word_img=\"file:///C:\\Users\\dev04\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\ksohtml\\wps8BD3.tmp.jpg\" style=\"background:url(http://localhost:8080/ueditor1_3_6/lang/zh-cn/images/localimage.png) no-repeat center center;border:1px solid #ddd\"/><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:69px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">⑥<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">.struts2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的后缀</span></span> <span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span><img width=\"554\" height=\"37\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor1_3_6/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" word_img=\"file:///C:\\Users\\dev04\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\ksohtml\\wps8BD4.tmp.jpg\" style=\"background:url(http://localhost:8080/ueditor1_3_6/themes/default/images/word.gif) no-repeat center center;border:1px solid #ddd\"/></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">这样写<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">比如就可以</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">index.do</span><span s